      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) in showroom condition. This example features the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six equipped with VarioCam Plus, mated to a crisp 6-speed G96 manual transaxle. The mechanical integrity is absolute, featuring a proactive IMS bearing retrofit and a flawless cooling system. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, supported by original Bilstein dampers and four-piston monoblock Brembo calipers. Every surface, from the deep-gloss paint to the supple leather interior, remains in a state of preservation that defies its age. With zero UV degradation and a comprehensive service dossier, this 911 provides the tactile steering feedback and linear power delivery that defines the analog driving era.",
